|1 |├─TABLE FULL SCAN        |t1   |1       |3           |
|2 |└─LIMIT                  |     |1       |6           |
|3 |  └─HASH RIGHT SEMI JOIN |     |1       |6           |
|4 |    ├─SUBPLAN SCAN       |VIEW1|1       |3           |
|5 |    │ └─TABLE FULL SCAN  |t3   |1       |3           |
|6 |    └─TABLE FULL SCAN    |t2   |1       |3           |
==========================================================
